OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be bright and
OL,6,Fmainly dry with some sunny spells but
OL,7,Fthere will be a scattering of light
OL,8,Fshowers in the north. The afternoon
OL,9,Fwill see any showers die out, with
OL,10,Flonger sunny spells. Mainly light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a fine dry and
OL,14,Fsunny evening. Some clear spells at
OL,15,Ffirst tonight but turning cloudier
OL,16,Fovernight, with perhaps the odd light
OL,17,Fshower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
