OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAny cloud breaking up to allow
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells, and becoming warm.
OL,7,FCloud and patchy rain spreading to the
OL,8,FIsles later in afternoon perhaps
OL,9,Freaching far north Highland in evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSome
OL,12,Fwarm sunshine on Tuesday but west
OL,13,Fclouding over with patchy rain. The
OL,14,Fwest cloudy on Wednesday, light
OL,15,Fshowers, east brighter, warmer. Some
OL,16,Fwarm sunshine Thursday but chance of
OL,17,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
